Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics.

Get Started Using CRM Analytics by Set Up the CRM Analytics Platform, Integrate Data into CRM Analytics Datasets, Gain Insights on Data Directly at Source.

Clone a Lens by clicking Clone in a New Tab from the More menu. A new, unsaved copy of the cloned lens opens in a new tab.

Build CRM Analytics Dashboards, Embed and Customize CRM Analytics, Create and Share CRM Analytics Apps, Deploy CRM Analytics Industry Apps and Prebuilt Apps, Develop with CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.
